name: Rogue paradox
description:
hello!

A game made for Black n White game jam!

controls:

a and d to move

left and right arrow key to move

w to jump up arrow key to jump

c to dash

e to use antigravity boots when equided anti gravity boots

story:

The Time Variance Authority(TVA) a agency who take care of timeline sends you to a misson to find the rogue the person who changed past and maked a mess.

this web game so you can play it without downloading it :)
